- compute validation probabilities with sigmoid
- if FINAL_SUBMISSION is true, after choosing the best cutoff, train a fresh final model on every labeled row currently loaded in train_df before test prediction
- compute test probabilities with sigmoid only if WRITE_SUBMISSION is true
- choose best cutoff by looping over np.linspace(threshold_min, threshold_max, threshold_steps)
- when WRITE_SUBMISSION is true, save columns id,target to submission_path
